export default <T extends unknown>(value: T) =>
  Array.isArray(value) ? value : [value];
sources.../src/utils/fillEmptyArray.ts:
export default <T>(value: T | T[]): undefined[] | undefined =>
  Array.isArray(value) ? value.map(() => undefined) : undefined;

export default (value: unknown): value is Function =>
  typeof value === 'function';

  value instanceof HTMLElement;

sources.../src/logic/getFieldValueAs.ts:
import { Field } from '../types';
import isUndefined from '../utils/isUndefined';

export default (
  value: any,
  { valueAsNumber, valueAsDate, setValueAs }: Field['_f'],
) =>
  isUndefined(value)
    ? value
    : valueAsNumber
    ? value === ''
      ? NaN
      : +value
    : valueAsDate
    ? new Date(value)
    : setValueAs
    ? setValueAs(value)
    : value;

import { Field } from '../types';

export default (options: Field['_f']) =>
  options.mount &&
  (options.required ||
    options.min ||
    options.max ||
    options.maxLength ||
    options.minLength ||
    options.pattern ||
    options.validate);
